{"id": "1340856360048529460", "channel_id": "1329362854721224704", "type": 19, "author_id": "191643200950239232", "author_name": "jadlithon", "author_bot": false, "content": "No I mean the ranges were before:\nNo Thais: 20-40, Thais: 30-60\nAnd now:\nNo Thais: 30-60, Thais: 45-90.", "timestamp": "2025-02-17T01:24:28.142000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["736441008145039421"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1340850012460023868", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1329362854721224704", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Tier list as of 2.0", "forum_channel_id": "1304022827824844842"}
{"id": "1340856542815322143", "channel_id": "1329362854721224704", "type": 0, "author_id": "191643200950239232", "author_name": "jadlithon", "author_bot": false, "content": "Remember that per-turn Embryo generation is also increased based on missing HP by up to 100% of the base gain, which means Thais' 50% increase affects that.", "timestamp": "2025-02-17T01:25:11.717000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1329362854721224704", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Tier list as of 2.0", "forum_channel_id": "1304022827824844842"}
{"id": "1340856871103234061", "channel_id": "1329362854721224704", "type": 0, "author_id": "736441008145039421", "author_name": "linireo", "author_bot": false, "content": "Ahh that's what you mean though honestly I still think e3 is the least impactful thing probably not worth getting at all", "timestamp": "2025-02-17T01:26:29.987000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1329362854721224704", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Tier list as of 2.0", "forum_channel_id": "1304022827824844842"}
